    <item>
      <title>银行客户损失 16 亿美元后泰国严厉打击金融欺诈行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/thailand-cracks-down-on-financial-fraud-after-bank-customers-lose-1-6-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行正在加大对用于网络金融诈骗的所谓“骡子账户”的打击力度，过去两年间，银行客户因此类诈骗损失了超过 600 亿泰铢（16 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/thailand-cracks-down-on-financial-fraud-after-bank-customers-lose-1-6-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 07:03:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典房东 SBB 计划在住房单元出售新债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/swedish-landlord-sbb-plans-to-sell-new-bonds-at-residential-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的瑞典房地产开发商 SBB 正准备将债券债务从母公司转移到 Sveafastigheter AB，为其整个住宅资产组合的首次公开募股 (IPO) 奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/swedish-landlord-sbb-plans-to-sell-new-bonds-at-residential-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 06:45:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>李克强总理访问新西兰 中国寻求加强与新西兰关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/china-seeks-stronger-ties-with-new-zealand-as-premier-li-visits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国国务院总理李强访问南太平洋国家新西兰的第一天，尽管双方承认存在分歧，但双方仍承诺加强经济联系。]]></description>
